  "html": "<p>Hey, ReFi Nation!</p><p>We're thrilled to bring you an exciting bonus episode of our podcast - \"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mHtsMVX4sgo&amp;t=2798s\">To Network State or Not to Network State</a>\" with <a href=\"https://twitter.com/MontyMerlin\">Monty Merlin</a>. In this special episode, we delve deep into the world of regeneration, Web3 technology, and the potential of a network state. Join us as we discuss the mission and vision of ReFi DAO and the broader movement for positive change. </p><p>You can <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mHtsMVX4sgo\">watch</a> or <a href=\"https://podfollow.com/1609683147/episode/24c69b014f838ddc2c751d0435e6acb3f7e0b238/view\">listen</a> to the full episode, or check out the <a href=\"__GHOST_URL__/to-network-state-refi-dao-forum/\">previous article</a> diving even deeper from the last <a href=\"https://www.refidao.com/community/working-group/ReFi-DAO-Forum/r/recbjJ1Wa9mZXW9JI\">ReFi DAO Forum</a> session.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-gallery-card kg-width-wide\"><div class=\"kg-gallery-container\"><div class=\"kg-gallery-row\"><div class=\"kg-gallery-image\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2023/07/What-is-a-Network-State--by-Balaji-Srinivasan---ReFi-DAO-1.jpg\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1125\" loading=\"lazy\" alt srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2023/07/What-is-a-Network-State--by-Balaji-Srinivasan---ReFi-DAO-1.jpg 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1000/2023/07/What-is-a-Network-State--by-Balaji-Srinivasan---ReFi-DAO-1.jpg 1000w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1600/2023/07/What-is-a-Network-State--by-Balaji-Srinivasan---ReFi-DAO-1.jpg 1600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w2400/2023/07/What-is-a-Network-State--by-Balaji-Srinivasan---ReFi-DAO-1.jpg 2400w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></div><div class=\"kg-gallery-image\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2023/08/To-Network-State-or-Not-to-Network-State---ReFi-Podcast-BONUS-2.png\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1119\" loading=\"lazy\" alt srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2023/08/To-Network-State-or-Not-to-Network-State---ReFi-Podcast-BONUS-2.png 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1000/2023/08/To-Network-State-or-Not-to-Network-State---ReFi-Podcast-BONUS-2.png 1000w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1600/2023/08/To-Network-State-or-Not-to-Network-State---ReFi-Podcast-BONUS-2.png 1600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w2400/2023/08/To-Network-State-or-Not-to-Network-State---ReFi-Podcast-BONUS-2.png 2400w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></div></div><div class=\"kg-gallery-row\"><div class=\"kg-gallery-image\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2023/08/image-10.png\" width=\"1315\" height=\"1110\" loading=\"lazy\" alt srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2023/08/image-10.png 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1000/2023/08/image-10.png 1000w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/2023/08/image-10.png 1315w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></div><div class=\"kg-gallery-image\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2023/08/image-9.png\" width=\"1600\" height=\"901\" loading=\"lazy\" alt srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2023/08/image-9.png 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1000/2023/08/image-9.png 1000w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/2023/08/image-9.png 1600w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></div></div></div></figure><p><em>But first, if you have enjoyed our content or resonate with the mission of ReFi DAO, we would be super grateful if you might consider <a href=\"https://explorer.gitcoin.co/#/round/10/0x2871742b184633f8dc8546c6301cbc209945033e/0x2871742b184633f8dc8546c6301cbc209945033e-179\">supporting us on Gitcoin</a>!</em></p><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://explorer.gitcoin.co/#/round/10/0x2871742b184633f8dc8546c6301cbc209945033e/0x2871742b184633f8dc8546c6301cbc209945033e-179\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Support ReFi DAO</a></div><p>Now on to the episo