\" y=\"1\" width=\"7\" height=\"22\" rx=\"1.5\" ry=\"1.5\"/></svg></button><span class=\"kg-video-current-time\">0:00</span><div class=\"kg-video-time\">/<span class=\"kg-video-duration\"></span></div><input type=\"range\" class=\"kg-video-seek-slider\" max=\"100\" value=\"0\"><button class=\"kg-video-playback-rate\">1&#215;</button><button class=\"kg-video-unmute-icon\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M15.189 2.021a9.728 9.728 0 0 0-7.924 4.85.249.249 0 0 1-.221.133H5.25a3 3 0 0 0-3 3v2a3 3 0 0 0 3 3h1.794a.249.249 0 0 1 .221.133 9.73 9.73 0 0 0 7.924 4.85h.06a1 1 0 0 0 1-1V3.02a1 1 0 0 0-1.06-.998Z\"/></svg></button><button class=\"kg-video-mute-icon kg-video-hide\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M16.177 4.3a.248.248 0 0 0 .073-.176v-1.1a1 1 0 0 0-1.061-1 9.728 9.728 0 0 0-7.924 4.85.249.249 0 0 1-.221.133H5.25a3 3 0 0 0-3 3v2a3 3 0 0 0 3 3h.114a.251.251 0 0 0 .177-.073ZM23.707 1.706A1 1 0 0 0 22.293.292l-22 22a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.414l.009.009a1 1 0 0 0 1.405-.009l6.63-6.631A.251.251 0 0 1 8.515 17a.245.245 0 0 1 .177.075 10.081 10.081 0 0 0 6.5 2.92 1 1 0 0 0 1.061-1V9.266a.247.247 0 0 1 .073-.176Z\"/></svg></button><input type=\"range\" class=\"kg-video-volume-slider\" max=\"100\" value=\"100\"></div></div></div></figure><h2 id=\"part-2-bridging-the-gap\">Part 2: Bridging the Gap</h2><p><a href=\"https://twitter.com/MontyMerlin\">Monty</a> and <a href=\"https://twitter.com/climateXcrypto\">John</a> reflect on their backgrounds and early childhood experiences that shaped their dedication to the environment and positive impact. They discuss the limitations of existing systems and institutions, and highlight the urgency of finding solutions for global coordination to address the pressing issues facing humanity and the planet.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><iframe width=\"200\" height=\"113\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/vT1dLkGA1xM?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen title=\"Without ACTION, everything else is MEANINGLESS #refi #carboncredits #regeneration #climateaction\"></iframe></figure><figure class=\"kg-card kg-video-card\"><div class=\"kg-video-container\"><video src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/media/2023/08/ReFi-Podcast-Clip--There-is-somthing-fundamentally-wrong--2.mp4\" poster=\"https://img.spacergif.org/v1/1280x720/0a/spacer.png\" width=\"1280\" height=\"720\" playsinline preload=\"metadata\" style=\"background: transparent url('__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2023/08/media-thumbnail-ember257.jpg') 50% 50% / cover no-repeat;\" /></video><div class=\"kg-video-overlay\"><button class=\"kg-video-large-play-icon\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M23.14 10.608 2.253.164A1.559 1.559 0 0 0 0 1.557v20.887a1.558 1.558 0 0 0 2.253 1.392L23.14 13.393a1.557 1.557 0 0 0 0-2.785Z\"/></svg></button></div><div class=\"kg-video-player-container\"><div class=\"kg-video-player\"><button class=\"kg-video-play-icon\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M23.14 10.608 2.253.164A1.559 1.559 0 0 0 0 1.557v20.887a1.558 1.558 0 0 0 2.253 1.392L23.14 13.393a1.557 1.557 0 0 0 0-2.785Z\"/></svg></button><button class=\"kg-video-pause-icon kg-video-hide\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><rect x=\"3\" y=\"1\" width=\"7\" height=\"22\" rx=\"1.5\" ry=\"1.5\"/><rect x=\"14\" y=\"1\" width=\"7\" height=\"22\" rx=\"1.5\" ry=\"1.5\"/></svg></button><span class=\"kg-video-current-time\">0:00</span><div class=\"kg-video-time\">/<span class=\"kg-video-duration\"></span></div><input type=\"range\" class=\"kg-video-seek-slider\" max=\"100\" value=\"0\"><button class=\"kg-video-playback-rate\">1&#215;</button><button class=\"kg-video-unmute-icon\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M15.189 2.021a9.728 9.728 0 0 0-7.924 4.85.249.249 0 0 1-.221.133H5.25a3 3 0 0 0-3 3v2a3 3 0 0 0 3 3h1.794a.249.249 0 0 1 .221.133 9.73 9.73 0 0 0 7.924 4.85h.06a1 1 0 0 0 1-1V3.02a1 1 0 0 0-1.06-.998Z\"/></svg></button><button class=\"kg-video-mute-icon kg-video-hide\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M16.177 4.3a.248.248 0 0 0 .073-.176v-1.1a1 1 0 0 0-1.061-1 9.728 9.728 0 0 0-7.924 4.85.249.249 0 0 1-.221.133H5.25a3 3 0 0 0-3 3v2a3 3 0 0 0 3 3h.114a.251.251 0 0 0 .177-.073ZM23.707 1.706A1 1 0 0 0 22.293.292l-22 22a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.414l.009.009a1 1 0 0 0 1.405-.009l6.63-6.631A.251.251 0 0 1 8.515 17a.245.245 0 0 1 .177.075 10.081 10.081 0 0 0 6.5 2.92 1 1 0 0 0 1.061-1V9.266a.247.247 0 0 1 .073-.176Z\"/></svg></button><input type=\"range\" class=\"kg-video-volume-slider\" max=\"100\" value=\"100\"></div></div></div></figure><h2 id=\"part-3-the-power-of-collaboration\">Part 3: The Power of Collaboration</h2><p>The discussion evolves to the importance of collaboration and building bridges between various networks and communities. They explore the value of pluralism in designing solutions and how diverse communities can contribute to a common goal. Monty unveils exciting plans for cross-network collaboration and shared initiatives that will empower individuals to make a real impact, regardless of their level of familiarity with the Web3 space.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><iframe width=\"200\" height=\"113\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/zwdXxA1T96Q?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen title=\"A network of coordiNATIONs ‚Äî an evolution of Balaji&#39;s Network State concept\"></iframe></figure><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><iframe width=\"200\" height=\"113\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/SguHnbLnlGA?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen title=\"Local Regeneration Enabled by Web3 #regeneration #refi #crypto #climateaction\"></iframe></figure><h2 id=\"part-4-building-for-the-future\">Part 4: Building for the Future</h2><p>As the conversation comes to a close, Monty and John share their visions for the future. They discuss the necessity of building strong foundations, both in terms of technology and community, especially during bear markets. They stress the significance of storytelling in driving attention and engagement within the Web3 movement. With an optimistic outlook, they invite listeners to join the movement, participate in events, and contribute to the shared vision of regeneration and positive change!</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-gallery-card kg-width-wide\"><div class=\"kg-gallery-container\"><div class=\"kg-gallery-row\"><div class=\"kg-gallery-image\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2023/08/Regen-CoordiNATION---ReFi-DAO.png\" width=\"1838\" height=\"1032\" loading=\"lazy\" alt srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2023/08/Regen-CoordiNATION---ReFi-DAO.png 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1000/2023/08/Regen-CoordiNATION---ReFi-DAO.png 1000w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1600/2023/08/Regen-CoordiNATION---ReFi-DAO.png 1600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/2023/08/Regen-CoordiNATION---ReFi-DAO.png 1838w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></div><div class=\"kg-gallery-image\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2023/08/ReFi-DAO---Regenerate-the-entire-economy.png\" width=\"1802\" height=\"1050\" loading=\"lazy\" alt srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2023/08/ReFi-DAO---Regenerate-the-entire-economy.png 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1000/2023/08/ReFi-DAO---Regenerate-the-entire-economy.png 1000w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1600/2023/08/ReFi-DAO---Regenerate-the-entire-economy.png 1600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/2023/08/ReFi-DAO---Regenerate-the-entire-